  "texts": [
    "The supernatants were then filtered through the RP18 SPE columns (activated by elution of 1 mL acetonitrile and equilibrated by elution 1 mL methanol/ acetonitrile/H 2 O (5/3/2, v/v/v) before usage) after centrifugation (5 min, 16,000 × g, 4 °C).",
    "The eluents were collected and mixed with 400 µL of methanol/acetonitrile/H 2 O (5/3/2, v/v/v).",
    "The mixtures were vortexed, ultrasound, centrifuged, and filtered as before and the eluent was collected and evaporated in SpeedVac overnight at 15 °C.",
    "Samples were stored at -80 °C.",
    "The lipids in the culture medium were extracted with methanol and chloroform."
